DenisDutton_2010 1 DenisDutton_2010 735.34 743.05 <o,f0,male> fine motor control planning ability conscientiousness and sometimes access to rare materials
DenisDutton_2010 1 DenisDutton_2010 754.39 757.80 <o,f0,male> you know it's an old line but it has been shown to work
DenisDutton_2010 1 DenisDutton_2010 758.82 761.89 <o,f0,male> come up to my cave so i can show you my hand axes
DenisDutton_2010 1 DenisDutton_2010 764.03 770.82 <o,f0,male> except of course what's interesting about this is that we can't be sure how that idea was conveyed because the
