DenisDutton_2010 1 DenisDutton_2010 790.50 795.42 <o,f0,male> between fifty and one hundred thousand years before language
DenisDutton_2010 1 DenisDutton_2010 806.35 816.78 <o,f0,male> by the end of the hand axe epic homo sapiens as they were then called finally were doubtless finding new ways to amuse and amaze each other
DenisDutton_2010 1 DenisDutton_2010 817.41 824.03 <o,f0,male> who knows telling jokes storytelling dancing or hairstyling yes hairstyling i insist on that
DenisDutton_2010 1 DenisDutton_2010 825.51 837.48 <o,f0,male> for us moderns virtuoso technique is used to create imaginary worlds in fiction and in movies to express intense emotions with music painting and dance
DenisDutton_2010 1 DenisDutton_2010 837.98 846.50 <o,f0,male> but still one fundamental trait of the ancestral personality persists in our aesthetic cravings
DenisDutton_2010 1 DenisDutton_2010 847.04 854.56 <o,f0,male> the beauty we find in skilled performances from lascaux to the louvre to carnegie hall
DenisDutton_2010 1 DenisDutton_2010 855.28 861.84 <o,f0,male> human beings have a permanent innate taste for virtuoso displays in the arts
DenisDutton_2010 1 DenisDutton_2010 862.90 867.14 <o,f0,male> we find beauty in something done well
